Cosmos Installer Images
=======================

Required images for the Inno Setup Windows installer:

- cosmos.bmp      - Wizard sidebar image (164x314 pixels, 24-bit BMP)
- cosmos_small.bmp - Small wizard image (55x55 pixels, 24-bit BMP)
- cosmos.ico       - Application icon (.ico format, 256x256 recommended)

These can be generated from the Cosmos logo or any branding artwork.
If images are missing, remove the WizardImageFile, WizardSmallImageFile,
and SetupIconFile lines from Cosmos.iss to use Inno Setup defaults.
